---
/**
 * HypoHowItWorksScreen — "How Hypo Shield works" education (v0.4). The ONE
 * place the feature is explained, linked from the Learning State card,
 * Settings · Hypo Shield, and the recommendation takeover — so individual
 * screens never have to repeat it. This is also the single spot where the
 * clinical term appears: "total daily basal dose (TDBD)", as a parenthetical
 * mapping to what clinicians say. Pushed detail (Moonlight back), no tab bar.
 */
interface Props { variant?: "current" | "legacy"; }
---
<div class="content" style="overflow-y:auto;">
  <div class="navbar">
    <button class="back" aria-label="Back">
      <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M15 18l-6-6 6-6"/></svg>
      Hypo Shield
    </button>
  </div>
  <div class="pad" style="padding-bottom:10px;"><h1 style="margin:0; font-size:28px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.015em; color:var(--color-on-dark);">How Hypo Shield works</h1></div>

  <div class="pad hiw">
    <div class="sec-label">What it is</div>
    <div class="card-dark hiw-card">
      <p>Hypo Shield watches your nighttime glucose and learns how well your <b>long-acting insulin</b> — what your care team may call your total daily basal dose (TDBD) — matches your overnight needs.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="sec-label">How it learns</div>
    <div class="card-dark hiw-card">
      <p>Luna learns from <b>7 days of wear and 5 Luna sessions</b> before suggesting anything. While it learns, dosing stays a little more conservative. If you change your dose manually, learning starts over around the new dose.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="sec-label">What it does</div>
    <div class="card-dark hiw-card">
      <p>When your long-acting dose looks mis-set, Hypo Shield <b>suggests</b> a corrected dose and explains why. It never changes your dose, your settings, or delivers anything on its own.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="sec-label">What you do</div>
    <div class="card-dark hiw-card">
      <p>You review the suggestion, and if you agree you do both: <b>update the dose in Luna's settings</b> and <b>take the new dose yourself</b>. You can skip any suggestion — it waits for you under Settings · Hypo Shield.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="height:16px;"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<style is:global>
  .ux-ios .hiw .hiw-card { padding: 15px 16px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .ux-ios .hiw .hiw-card p { margin: 0; font-size: 13.5px; line-height: 1.55; color: var(--color-on-dark-sub); }
  .ux-ios .hiw .hiw-card p b { color: var(--color-on-dark); font-weight: 700; }
  .ux-ios .hiw .sec-label { margin-top: 14px; }
</style>
